start HAL on liono (orange)
cd ~/gaps/build/hal/test/sync
../../daemon/hal -l 0 ./sync_orange.cfg

start HAL on jaga (green)
cd ~/gaps/build/hal/test/sync
../../daemon/hal -l 0 ./sync_green.cfg

generating hal configuration
----------------------------
from ~/gaps/build/hal/test/sync, run the fllowing

1. cp ~/gaps/build/apps/sync/partitioned/multithreaded/xdconf.ini .

2. ../../confgen/hal_autoconfig.py -d ../../confgen/device_defs/devices_jaga_liono.json -x ./xdconf.ini -p sync -o .

